 fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gerando Subconjuntos</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Nossa primeira aplicação da recursão será gerar todos os subconjuntos de um conjunto de N elementos;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"gerando-permutações\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gerando-permuta%C3%A7%C3%B5es\" aria-label=\"gerando permutações permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gerando Permutações</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>A segunda aplicação de recursão que veremos será gerar todas as permutações de um conjunto de N elementos;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"desafio\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#desafio\" aria-label=\"desafio permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Desafio</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/645/A\">Amity Assessment</a> - Codeforces\n<ul>\n<li>Generalizar a solução do problema para 2 ≤ N ≤ 10, elencando todas as possíveis soluções do quebra-cabeças com um algoritmo recursivo.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"backtracking\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#backtracking\" aria-label=\"backtracking permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Backtracking</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Aperfeiçoamento do algoritmo de força bruta;</li>\n<li>Várias soluções da força bruta são eliminadas, visto que não são testadas;</li>\n<li>Inicialmente se tem uma solução vazia e vamos estendendo ela passo apasso, incrementalmente.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"problema-das-rainhas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#problema-das-rainhas\" aria-label=\"problema das rainhas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Problema das Rainhas</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Calcular o número de maneiras de se colocar N rainhas em um tabuleiro NxN.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Em um problema de backtracking inicia-se com uma solução vazia, nesse caso com o tabuleiro vazio.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>A partir do tabuleiro vazio a solução é estendida passo a passo até que se consiga colocar todas as N rainhas.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Confira a GIF abaixo:</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/static/gif2-778fdadbe83413e94e74840d1d153c66.gif\" alt=\"img13 - img42\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-cpp line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> ll<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nvector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">bool</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> diagonal<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> diagonal2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> coluna<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> linha<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nll n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nll cont <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">colocar_rainha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ll lin<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ll col<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lin <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        cont<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>col <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>diagonal<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lin <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> col<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> diagonal2<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>lin<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> \n        <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> coluna<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> linha<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>lin<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">colocar_rainha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lin<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> col<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">colocar_rainha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lin<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"sugestão-de-problemas-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sugest%C3%A3o-de-problemas-1\" aria-label=\"sugestão de problemas 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sugestão de Problemas</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cses.fi/problemset/task/1624\">Chessboard and Queens</a> - CSES</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.spoj.com/problems/MKJUMPS/\">MKJUMPS</a> - SPOJ</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"problema-do-labirinto\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#problema-do-labirinto\" aria-label=\"problema do labirinto permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Problema do Labirinto</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Encontrar um caminho da entrada do labirinto até a saída.</li>\n<li>Gerar a solução por partes, e quando encontrarmos em um beco sem saída, retornar os passos até que se possa ter acesso à outro caminho.</li>\n<li>Confira na GIF abaixo:</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/static/gif3-fa0252c83862be4e028efa0ff8021abf.gif\" alt=\"img45 - img72\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-cpp line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> ll<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nvector<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>pair<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ll<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>ll<span class=\"token operator\">>></span> mov <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</sp